msgid "You will then see your building as a a solid shape with the inner polygons represented with gaps. The data behind the relation in this example is visible on OpenStreetMap: You can see this multipologyon on OSM by going to http://www.openstreetmap.org/browse/relation/2435797. It will appear on OpenStreetMap like this:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/training/intermediate/osm/301-advanced-editing.rst:299
